_sText:
known bug: If your lamp and lit on a gray wall, you'll see the skybox and you could not see very far. Switch off the light and the bug disappear.

Note: There is a line in a cell, those leads can teleport a single person per round, this limit is set to teleport to avoid a rush of terrorism in the armory.

Max player : 50 (20 ct and 30 t)
